description:
Penny and Cheyenne perform flawlessly today under their coach's instruction. Dragon is finally catching a break this season. They dominate Nightmare for this match and score some much needed points going into the finals Next month.
That's right. The Tag Team Season 10 finals will be shot Next month LIVE August 2nd 7PM PST. Dragon needed the points from today's win. The new score is Nightmare: 5230 Dragon: 4818
August 2nd is our first tag match in the new set. It is the BIGGEST TAG MATCH is US history.
Syd will be out of the country but she hand picked Jayogen to step in as captain in her absence. The other members of Team nightmare that will be pressent include:
Jayogen
Darling
Bella Wilde
Bella Rossi
Isamar
Berretta James
For team Dragon:
Dragon lily
cheyenne Jewel
Penny Barber
Daisy Ducati
serena Blair
and filling in for mistress Kara, Sophia Fiore ORGASMS WORTH TWICE AS MANY POINTS
Each girl wrestles with a partner of her team for 1 round. This means the action will be fast and furious as no one will gas out. It also means there will be NO breaks between wrestling rounds, We will shoot the wrestling straight through so viewers at home don't lose interest between rounds.
This also means there is a massive gang bang at the end.
Tune in LIVE Aug 2nd 7pm PST!!
title: Dragon Maintains Lead for this Match. Big time Catch up done today
